
Timestamp: When the event occurred.
Log Level (optional): Severity of the message (e.g., INFO, ERROR, DEBUG, WARNING).
Component Name (e.g., EA Name): Identifies the source of the log.
Context (e.g., Symbol): Relevant trading pair or asset.
Message: Detailed information about the event.



void Log(string message)
{
    Print(StringFormat("[%s][%s][%s][%s] %s", TimeToString(TimeCurrent(), TIME_DATE | TIME_MINUTES), "INFO", EA_NAME, _Symbol, message));
}